# REQUIRES: tianchenrv-local-rvv-object-clang
#
# P-B6 (the deferred-wide bundle-export landing; un-XFAIL'd from P-B5). The byte
# (unpacked) widening_product_reduce_dequantize_f32 kernel realizes the DEFERRED-
# WIDE winner at the real architectural vector-register budget (32) via the
# resource-aware selector, and the description/bundle-export engine now RECOGNIZES
# the deferred-wide body (the widening_accumulate compute step + the i8m2/i16m4/
# i32m8 wide ladder) and produces the PARALLEL deferred-wide fact set, so the wide
# byte kernel exports a valid target-artifact bundle (.o + .h). The WPRD-DAG block
# below asserts the honest WIDE facts (the deferred chain, the wide strip ladder
# src-i8m2, the i32m8 deferred accumulate carry). The same-logical route identity /
# leaf profile / ABI prototype are unchanged. The wide single-scope body emits NO
# low_precision_resource.* selection block and NO gearbox_cross_region_handoff
# (those are the narrow grouped two-scope candidate artifacts) -- the wide path's
# facts are the primitive-facts ladder, asserted honestly here (I5: the wide body
# is authority). The runnable-C winner is ssh-rvv numeric-validated + measured
# (P-B5 灯: 4.1-10.8x vs scalar, 3.3-5.4x vs naive).
# RUN: rm -rf %t.artifacts
# RUN: python3 %S/../../scripts/rvv_generated_bundle_abi_e2e.py --dry-run --pre-realized-selected-body --artifact-root %t.artifacts --run-id pre-realized-widening-product-reduce-dequantize-f32 --overwrite --op-kind widening_product_reduce_dequantize_f32 --runtime-count 0 --runtime-count 1 --runtime-count 16 --runtime-count 17 --runtime-count 257 --tcrv-opt tcrv-opt --tcrv-translate tcrv-translate --llvm-readobj llvm-readobj | FileCheck %s --check-prefix=STDOUT
# RUN: FileCheck %s --check-prefix=ROOT < %t.artifacts/pre-realized-widening-product-reduce-dequantize-f32/evidence.json
# RUN: FileCheck %s --check-prefix=WPRD --implicit-check-not="descriptor" --implicit-check-not="direct-C" --implicit-check-not="source-export" --implicit-check-not="tcrv_rvv.i32_" --implicit-check-not="low_precision_resource.selected_candidate" --implicit-check-not="gearbox_cross_region_handoff" --implicit-check-not="gearbox.producer_scope" < %t.artifacts/pre-realized-widening-product-reduce-dequantize-f32/widening_product_reduce_dequantize_f32/evidence.json
# RUN: FileCheck %s --check-prefix=HARNESS --implicit-check-not="descriptor" --implicit-check-not="direct-C" --implicit-check-not="source-export" < %t.artifacts/pre-realized-widening-product-reduce-dequantize-f32/widening_product_reduce_dequantize_f32/rvv_generated_bundle_abi_widening_product_reduce_dequantize_f32_harness.c

